-# What's the difference between a photo essay supplemental, and a regular supplemental?
-# Not a whole lot. The biggest difference is the teaser graphic (take special note of the header element)
-# The metadata is different too, as a photo essay won't have a "Get Text" option
-# Other than that, things are pretty similar!

